   Please visit the Programs and Projects page to find links to the USGS
   programs focused on the habitat and resources of the Bay. The Data page
   gives information and links on various USGS data and spatial
   information sites concerned with the Bay area and its associated
   habitats.

   We welcome comments and suggestions on this redesigned site.

